_header: Hail Winifred that worshipful with thy virginity
_description: John Audelay, ‘Salutacio Sancte Wenefrede virginisi’ — seven 9-line stanzas

BodDou302.First Lines:
Hayle wenefryd þat worchipful with þi vergeneteHayl
                    meruelus marter & merceful may…
BodDou302.Last Lines:
…þat we be neuer chamyd ne chendWe pray þe
                    Wenefryde
BodDou302.Attributed Title:
Hic incipit Salutacio Sancte Wenefrede virginis (f. 26v);
                        Explicit salutacio (f. 27b)
